// Social Proof component
---

<section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        Trusted by Open Source Community
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
        Join developers worldwide using KodeOps to automate their SDLC
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mb-16 text-center">
      <div>
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-2">1,000+</div>
        <div class="text-gray-600">GitHub Stars</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-2">50+</div>
        <div class="text-gray-600">Contributors</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-2">100+</div>
        <div class="text-gray-600">Projects Using KodeOps</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-2">MIT</div>
        <div class="text-gray-600">Open Source License</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonials -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-semibold">AC</span>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-3">
            <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Alex Chen</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Senior Engineer, TechCorp</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          "KodeOps transformed our planning process. What used to take 3 weeks now takes 30 minutes. 
          Love that it's open source so we can contribute back to the community."
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-green-600 font-semibold">JM</span>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-3">
            <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Jordan Martinez</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">DevOps Engineer, StartupXYZ</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          "The persistent memory feature is game-changing. KodeOps remembers every decision 
          and context. Being open source means we can extend it for our specific needs."
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-purple-600 font-semibold">TK</span>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-3">
            <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Taylor Kim</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Engineering Lead, ScaleUp Inc</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          "Our team velocity increased 40% after adopting KodeOps. The automated business 
          reviews give executives perfect visibility into our progress."
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
